10px; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none;\"><p>2002.02--2003.02</p></td>\n   <td style=\"padding: 5px 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none;\"><p>澳大利亚墨尔本大学地球科学学院 访问学者</p></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"padding: 5px 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none;\"><p>2001.09--2016.07</p></td>\n   <td style=\"padding: 5px 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none;\"><p>北京大学地球与空间科学学院 副教授</p></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"padding: 5px 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none;\"><p>2016.08--至今</p></td>\n   <td style=\"padding: 5px 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none;\"><p>北京大学地球与空间科学学院 教授</p></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table></div></div><div class=\"fl02 clearfix\"> <div class=\"title002 clearfix\"><font>承担项目</font></div> <div class=\"ar_article\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">pop'</p></div></div><div class=\"fl02 clearfix\"> <div class=\"title002 clearfix\"><font>学术成果</font></div> <div class=\"ar_article\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">1. Yan Chen, Zhicheng Zhang*, C. Mark Fanning, Jinfu Yang, Bin Fu, Tairan Wu. Geochemistry and zircon U-Pb-Hf isotopic data for Permo-Carboniferous sediments in the Solonker Zone, Inner Mongolia, China: constraints on depositional age, provenance and tectonic setting. Journal of the Geological Society of London, doi: 10.1144/jgs2017-079</p>\n<p>2. Zejia Ji, Zhicheng Zhang*, Baofu Han, Haifei Yu, Yan Chen. Zircon U-Pb-Hf isotopes and geochemistry analyses of Huyu dykes from northwest of Beijing, China: New evidence for the initial destruction of the North China Craton. International Geology Review, 2018, 60(2): 196-216</p>\n<p>3. 钱筱嫣, 张志诚*, 陈彦, 于海飞, 杨金福, 罗志文. 内蒙古朱日和地区早古生代岩浆岩年代学、地球化学特征及其构造意义. 地球科学, 2017, 42(9): 1472-1494. DOI：10.3799/dqkx.2017.545</p>\n<p>4. Jinfu Yang, Zhicheng Zhang*, Yan Chen, Haifei Yu, Xiaoyan Qian. Ages and origin of felsic rocks from the Eastern Erenhot ophiolitic complex, southeastern Central Asian Orogenic Belt, Inner Mongolia China.. Journal of Asian Earth Sciences, 2017, 2017, 144: 126-140</p>\n<p>5. Lixia Feng, Roderick W. Brown, Baofu Han, Zengzhen Wang, Katarzyna Łuszczak, Bo Liu, Zhicheng Zhang, Jianqing Ji. Thrusting and exhumation of the southern Mongolian Plateau: Joint thermochronological constraints from the Langshan Mountains, western Inner Mongolia, China. Journal of Asian Earth Sciences, 2017, 144: 287–302</p>\n<p>6. Zhicheng Zhang, Yan Chen, Ke Li, Jianfeng Li, Jinfu Yang, Xiaoyan Qian. Geochronology and geochemistry of Permian bimodal volcanic rocks from central Inner Mongolia, China: Implications for the late Palaeozoic tectonic evolution of the south-eastern Central Asian Orogenic Belt. Journal of Asian Earth Sciences, 2017, 135, 370–389</p>\n<p>7. Yan Chen, Zhicheng Zhang*, Ke Li, Qiugen Li, Zhiwen Luo. Provenance of the Middle Permian Zhesi Formation in central Inner Mongolia, Northern China: constraints from petrography, geochemistry and detrital zircon U–Pb geochronology. Geological Journal, 2017, 52: 92–109, doi: 10.1002/gj.2735</p>\n<p>8. Jianfeng Li, Zhicheng Zhang*, Yue Zhao, Junling Pei, Wenhao Tang, Ke Li. Detrital apatite fission track analyses of the Subei basin: implications for basin-range structure of the northern Tibetan Plateau. International Geology Review, 2017, 59(2): 204–218, doi:10.1080/00206814.2016.1219880</p>\n<p>9. Yan Chen, Zhicheng Zhang*, Ke Li, Haifei Yu, Tairan Wu. Geochemistry and zircon U-Pb-Hf isotopes of early-Paleozoic-Sonid Zuoqi-arc-related volcanic rocks: Implications for the tectonic evolution of the southeastern Central Asian Orogenic Belt. Lithos, 2016, 264: 392–404,10.1016/j.lithos.2016.09.009</p>\n<p>10. Yan Chen, Zhicheng Zhang*, Ke Li, Haifei Yu, Tairan Wu. Detrital zircon U–Pb ages and Hf isotopes of Permo-Carboniferous sandstones in central Inner Mongolia, China: Implications for provenance and tectonic evolution of the southeastern Central Asian Orogenic Belt. Tectonophysics, 2016, 671: 183-201, DOI: 10.1016/j.tecto.2016.01.018</p>\n<p>11. 于海飞, 张志诚*, 帅歌伟, 陈彦, 汤文豪. 北京十三陵-西山髫髻山组火山岩年龄及其地质意义. 地质论评, 2016, 62(4): 807-826</p>\n<p>12. Zhiwen Luo, Zhicheng Zhang*, Ke Li, Jianfeng Li, Wenhao Tang, Bei Xu. Petrography, geochemistry, and U–Pb detrital zircon dating of Early Permian sedimentary rocks from the North Flank of the North China Craton: Implications for the Late Paleozoic tectonic evolution of the eastern Central Asian Orogenic Belt. International Geology Review, 2016, 58(7): 787-806,doi:10.1080/00206814.2015.1118646</p>\n<p>13. Ke Li, Marc Jolivet, Zhicheng Zhang*, Jianfeng Li, Wenhao Tang. Long–term exhumation history of the Inner Mongolian Plateau constrained by apatite fission track analysis. Tectonophysics, 2016, 666: 121-133, doi: 10.1016/j.tecto.2015.10.020</p>\n<p>14. Wenhao Tang, Zhicheng Zhang*, Jianfeng Li, Ke Li, Zhiwen Luo, Yan Chen. Mesozoic and Cenozoic uplift and exhumation of the Bogda Mountain, NW China: Evidence from apatite fission track analysis. Geoscience Frontiers, 2015, 6(4): 617-625, doi: 10.1016/j.gsf.2014.04.006</p>\n<p>15. 李可，张志诚**，冯志硕，李建锋，汤文豪，罗志文，陈彦. 兴蒙造山带中段北部晚古生代两期岩浆活动及其地质意义. 地质学报, 2015, 89(2): 272-288</p>\n<p>16. 罗志文, 张志诚*, 李建锋, 冯志硕, 汤文豪. 中南祁连西缘肃北三个洼塘地区古生代两类花岗质侵入岩年代学及其地质意义. 岩石学报, 2015, 31(1): 176-188</p>\n<p>17. Zhicheng Zhang, Ke Li, Jianfeng Li, Wenhao Tang, Yan Chen, Zhiwen Luo. Geochronology and geochemistry of the Eastern Erenhot ophiolitic complex: Implications for the tectonic evolution of the Inner Mongolia-Daxinganling Orogenic Belt. Journal of Asian Earth Sciences, 2015, 97: 279-293, doi: 10.1016/j.jseaes.2014.06.008</p>\n<p>18. Chen Chen, Zhicheng Zhang, Ke Li, Yan Chen, Wenhao Tang, Jianfeng Li. Geochronology, geochemistry, and its geological significance of the Damaoqi Permian volcanic sequences on the northern margin of the North China Block. Journal of Asian Earth Sciences, 2015, 97: 307-319, DOI: 10.1016/j.jseaes.2014.06.024</p>\n<p>19. 陈彦, 张志诚*, 李可, 罗志文, 汤文豪, 李秋根. 内蒙古苏尼特左旗北奥陶系砂岩物源分析及其地质意义. 地质通报, 2014, 33(9): 1308-1319</p>\n<p>20. 李可, 张志诚*, 冯志硕, 李建锋, 汤文豪, 罗志文. 内蒙古中部巴彦乌拉地区晚石炭世—早二叠世火山岩锆石SHRIMP U-Pb定年及其地质意义. 岩石学报, 2014, 30(7): 2041-2054</p>\n<p>21. 陈彦, 张志诚*, 李可, 罗志文, 汤文豪, 李秋根. 内蒙古西乌旗地区二叠纪双峰式火山岩的年代学、地球化学特征和地质意义. 北京大学学报(自然科学版), 2014, 50(5): 843-858. doi: 10.13209/j.0479-8023.2014.088</p>\n<p>22. Wenhao Tang, Zhicheng Zhang*, Jianfeng Li, Ke Li, Yan Chen, Zhaojie Guo. Late Paleozoic to Jurassic tectonic evolution of the Bogda area (northwest China): Evidence from detrital zircon U–Pb geochronology. Tectonophysics, 2014, 626: 144-156, doi.org/10.1016/j.tecto.2014.04.005</p>\n<p>23. Jianfeng Li, Zhicheng Zhang*, Wenhao Tang, Ke Li, Zhiwen Luo, Jie Li. Provenance of Oligocene–Miocene sediments in the Subei area, eastern Altyn Tagh fault and its geological implications: Evidence from detrital zircons LA-ICP-MS U–Pb chronology. Journal of Asian Earth Sciences, 2014, 87: 130-140</p>\n<p>24. 冯丽霞, 张志诚, 韩宝福, 任 荣, 李建锋 苏 犁.内蒙古达茂旗花岗岩类LA-ICP-MS 锆石U-Pb年龄及其地质意义[J]. 地质通报, 2013, 32(11): 1737-1748</p>\n<p>25. Wei Yang, Marc Jolivet, Guillaume Dupont-Nivet, Zhaojie Guo, Zhicheng Zhang and Chaodong Wu. Source to sink relations between theTian Shan and Junggar Basin (northwest China) from Late Palaeozoic to Quaternary: evidence from detrital U-Pb zircon geochronology. Basin Research, 2013, 25, 219–240, doi: 10.1111/j.1365-2117.2012.00558.x</p>\n<p>26. 刘冬冬, 郭召杰, 张志诚, 吴朝东. 准噶尔南缘古生代晚期盆山关系: 阿尔巴萨依组火山岩锆石SHRIMP U-Pb定年及岩石地球化学限定. 岩石学报, 2012, 28(8): 2355-2368</p>\n<p>27. 李可, 张志诚*, 李建锋, 汤文豪, 冯志硕, 李秋根. 内蒙古西乌珠穆沁旗地区中生代中酸性火山岩SHRIMP 锆石U-Pb年龄和地球化学特征. 地质通报, 2012, 31(5): 671-685</p>\n<p>28. 汤文豪, 张志诚*, 李建锋, 晨辰, 李可. 阿尔金断裂东端白垩纪火山岩地球化学特征及其地质意义. 地学前缘, 2012, 19(4): 51-62</p>\n<p>29. 张志诚, 郭召杰, 李建锋, 汤文豪. 阿尔金断裂带中段中新生代隆升历史分析：裂变径迹年龄制约. 第四纪研究, 2012, 32(3): 499-509</p>\n<p>30. 晨辰, 张志诚*, 郭召杰, 李建锋, 冯志硕, 汤文豪. 内蒙古达茂旗满都拉地区早二叠世基性岩的年代学、地球化学及其地质意义. 中国科学: 地球科学, 2012, 42(3): 343 ~ 358(通讯联系人)</p>\n<p>31. Chen Chen, Zhang Zhicheng*, Guo Zhaojie, Li Jianfeng, Feng Zhishuo, Tang Wenhao. 2012. Geochronology, geochemistry, and its geological significance of the Permian Mandula mafic rocks in Damaoqi, Inner Mongolia. Science China Earth Sciences, 55(1): 39-52(通讯联系人)</p>\n<p>32. 任荣, 韩宝福, 张志诚, 李建锋, 杨岳衡, 张艳斌. 北京昌平地区基底片麻岩和中-新元古代盖层锆石U-Pb年龄和Hf同位素研究及其地质意义. 岩石学报, 2011, 27(6): 1721-1745</p>\n<p>33. 于祥江, 季建清, 龚俊峰, 孙东霞, 庆建春, 王丽宁, 钟大赉, 张志诚. 雅鲁藏布大峡谷气候因素引起地壳剥蚀冷却的证据. 科学通报, 2011, 56(10): 765-773</p>\n<p>34. Yu XiangJiang, Ji JianQing, Gong JunFeng, et al. Evidences of rapid erosion driven by climate in the Yarlung Zangbo (Tsangpo) Great Canyon, the eastern Himalayan syntaxis. CHINESE SCIENCE BULLETIN, 2011, 56(11): 1123-1130 DOI: 10.1007/s11434-011-4419-x</p>\n<p>35. 郭召杰, 吴朝东, 张志诚, 陈伟. 准噶尔盆地南缘构造控藏作用及大型油气藏勘探方向浅析.高校地质学报, 2011, 17(2): 185-195</p>\n<p>36. 汤文豪, 张志诚*, 李建锋, 冯志硕, 晨辰. 内蒙古苏尼特右旗查干诺尔石炭系本巴图组火山岩地球化学特征及其地质意义. 北京大学学报(自然科学版), 2011, 47(2): 321-330(通讯联系人)</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">37. 李建锋, 汤文豪, 刘钊, 张志诚*. 北京千家店地区侏罗系后城组磷灰石裂变径迹分析及其地质意义. 地球物理学报, 2010, 53(12): 2907-2917, DOI: 10.3969/ j.issn.0001 -5733.2010. 12.0140(通讯联系人)</p></div></div><div class=\"fl02 clearfix\"> <div class=\"title002 clearfix\"><font>邀请报告</font></div> <div class=\"ar_article\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">暂无记录</p></div></div><div class=\"fl02 clearfix\"> <div class=\"title002 clearfix\"><font>获奖情况</font></div> <div class=\"ar_article\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">2003-2004 北京大学优秀班主任一等奖</p>\n<p>2008-2009 获北京大学教学成果一等奖</p>\n<p>2008-2009 获北京市教育教学成果（高等教育）二等奖</p>\n<p>2009-2010 获北京大学优秀共产党员荣誉称号</p>\n<p>2012-2013 获北京大学龙软科技优秀教师奖</p>\n<p>2013-2014 获北京大学宝钢优秀教师奖</p>\n<p>2014-2014 获教育部第三届高等学校自制实验教学仪器设备二等奖</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2016年Science China Earth Sciences 最佳论文奖</p></div></div><div class=\"fl02 clearfix\"> <div class=\"title002 clearfix\"><font>学术及社会任职</font></div> <div class=\"ar_article\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">1987- 至今 中国地质学会 会员</p>\n<p>1999-2001 国家自然科学基金委 地质学科项目主任</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2008- 至今 中国地质学会构造地质与地球动力学专业委员会 副秘书长</p></div></div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n\n\n    \n      \n    <p align=\"right\">【<a href=\"java